SEARCH
Package pl.prawko.prawko_server.model

Record Class QuestionCSV

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
pl.prawko.prawko_server.model.QuestionCSV
Record Components:
name - name of a question
id - fixed identifier
contentPL - translation of a question content in Polish
answerPL1 - content of first answer in Polish
answerPL2 - content of second answer in Polish
answerPL3 - content of third answer in Polish
contentEN - translation of question content in English
answerEN1 - content of first answer translation in English
answerEN2 - content of second answer translation in English
answerEN3 - content of third answer translation in English
contentDE - translation of a question content in German
answerDE1 - content of first answer translation in German
answerDE2 - content of second answer translation in German
answerDE3 - content of third answer translation in German
correctAnswer - label of correct answer - A, B, C and T, N which is Polish translation of Yes, No which stands for True and False
mediaName - filename of media attached to a question - .wmv | .jpg
type - question type - PODSTAWOWY or SPECJALISTYCZNY
value - score value of correct answer to a question
categories - categories to which the question belongs represented by comma-separated string
public record QuestionCSV(String name, int id, String contentPL, String answerPL1, String answerPL2, String answerPL3, String contentEN, String answerEN1, String answerEN2, String answerEN3, String contentDE, String answerDE1, String answerDE2, String answerDE3, char correctAnswer, String mediaName, String type, int value, String categories) extends Record
Represents single question from CSV file.
